1. install composer
2. apt-get install php5-dev php5-pear
3. pecl install mongodb
4. Edit /etc/php5/cli/php.ini tambahkan extension=mongo.so
5. composer update
6. bower install jquery
7. boser install bootstrap
8. set writable runtimme dan web/assets
9. bower install blueimp-gallery
10. bower install blueimp-canvas-to-blob
